"      www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/screening/ovarian/patient/",
"     </a>",
"     )",
"    </p>",
"    <p>",
"     <ul class=\"bullet-block\">",
"      <li>",
"       Medline Plus",
"      </li>",
